    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"it's temporary\" thing is just another way to delay the inevitable. you know as well as i do that the universe doesn't care. there's no grand plan or cosmic light waiting to fix things. it's just physics and void. why keep playing the game when the rules are rigged towards nothingness?",
